title: Age Of Empires 2 Gold Edition
description: This is an installer that I created myself after searching for this great game and not being able to find a good version of it anywhere. Just one .exe file and I made sure it's a clean install and uninstall, registry keys and all. Guaranteed working and virus free. This is the Gold Edition of the game which means it comes with The Conquerors expansion and some bonus maps already bundled in.
